data.description:
Assumable loan of $391,000 at a low-interest rate of 5.25%. 
Rare opportunity to own a new build with a quick move in. Located in the gated community of Stone Haven, is this gorgeous move in ready single story home. This beautiful home offers an open floor plan, plenty of cabinets, counter space and a large pantry. Spacious master bedroom features huge walk-in closet. The backyard is beautifully landscaped with synthetic grass and covered patio area for your enjoyment; which backs to a greenbelt offering complete privacy. 
You and your family will love the amenities offered in this community; from playgrounds to the community pool. 
To top it all off, this home is located minutes away from the State Farm Stadium and the Westgate entertainment district.
